OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixture of sunshine and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, some of these heavy
OL,7,Fand wintry at times. Feeling
OL,8,Funseasonably cold with a fresh north
OL,9,For northwesterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FLate sunny then clear spells
OL,12,Fand a few scattered showers, some of
OL,13,Fwhich may be wintry over higher
OL,14,Fground. A cold night with a touch of
OL,15,Ffrost.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA chilly but bright start
OL,18,Fto the day, some early sunny spells
OL,19,Fpossible. Turning rather cloudy with
OL,20,Fpatchy rain for a time in the
OL,21,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
